# ConversionHub Diagram Rules

## Subtext

- Subtext fits in **2 lines** with no truncation/ellipsis.
- Do NOT use `-webkit-line-clamp`. Card scales to fit (max-height: 10em, max-w: 280px).
- Use conversionhub-spoke-subtext; expand on group hover.

## Center Hub

- Icon: FileText only (h-8 w-8 / sm:h-10 sm:w-10). Label: "Structured Recipe."
- Ripple circles animate outward; connector dashes flow card→center.
